custom.deviceTagPath: [default]International/T1/Pier B/Apron/AMS Panel/AMS1 Genius Block Fault-LAN 3 Block 23

transforms.code:
substring = value.split('Block: ')[1]
	new_value = substring.split(' Genius')[0]
	return "BLK: " + new_value

substring = value.split('LAN: ')[1]
	new_value = substring.split(', Block')[0]
	return "LAN: " + new_value

substring = value.split('[')[1]
	new_value = substring.split(']')[0]
	return new_value
